		"description": {
			"value": "<div ><p><em>You toss a canister that bursts open, releasing a cloud of obscuring smoke.</em></p><p><span><strong>Utility Spell</strong></span></p><ul><li><p><span>You create a 5-foot-radius* sphere of smoke. The smoke spreads around corners.</span></p></li><li><p><span><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> The area is heavily obscured. Any amount of wind or water current that can push a creature will disperse the smoke early.</span></p></li></ul><p><span><br /></span></p><p><span><strong>*At Higher Levels:</strong> The maximum radius of the smoke increases by 5 ft. when you reach a total character or creature level of 5th level (10 ft.), 11th level (15 ft.), and 17th level (20 ft.). You can choose to make a smaller smoke field at these levels.</span></p>",
